Package scs1_group1.menu

Class DoctorMenu

Object
Menu
DoctorMenu
public class DoctorMenu extends Menu
The DoctorMenu class provides a menu interface for a doctor to interact with the system. It includes functions for managing appointments, setting availability, managing patient records, and viewing medical history.
